Installation instructions
-------------------------

To get xsvgen, first clone the git repository
% cd <your_dev_dir>
% git clone https://github.com/ANSSI-FR/xsvgen
% cd xsvgen

You must copy the config.mk template file and, if needed, adpat it to
your configuration (default values should work out of the box on
standard distributions):
% cp config.mk.tmpl config.mk
% vi config.mk

Finally, you may compile xsvgen:
% make
